01:40:22.720 --> 01:40:28.200
[Amit Varma]: or offline, probably online, and pick up The Emperor Who Never Was, Dara Shikoh in Mughal

01:40:28.200 --> 01:40:34.520
[Amit Varma]: India by Supriya Gandhi, magnificent storytelling, and it'll give you a much better sense of

01:40:34.520 --> 01:40:36.160
[Amit Varma]: the era that it covers.

